3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a method for reducing the complexity and power consumption of the system, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with millimeter wave communications, which is a subfield of multimedia. 
5. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture): The paper proposes a method for incorporating nested arrays into analog array architecture using RF switch networks, which is related to hardware architecture.
